                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1400-18420404 t18420404-1400-punishment-247"></join>Confined Three Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Sergeant.</hi>
